    {
      "id": "e97ec6c2-0b39-473d-b8aa-9474242efda2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Problem is student retention in self-paced educational programs. Authors use LSTM to predict student success and achieve remarkable results on OULAD - both when using the entire dataset (84.6% accuracy) and even when only using the first 5 weeks (71% accuracy). Authors also use Shapely to identify what are the most important predictors of student retention.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "e97ec6c2-0b39-473d-b8aa-9474242efda2",
