    {
      "id": "a0c5004a-f651-42f0-8dcc-834d9e39870d",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "There is smaller and smaller funding, so universities need inventive solutions to address the challenges they commonly face. Among such problems is student retention - failing and, in the most extreme cases, not concluding the cycle of studes at all. Early prediction is something that is attempted by institutions for multiple reasons: both pedagogical and administrative.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "a0c5004a-f651-42f0-8dcc-834d9e39870d",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
