    {
      "id": "beb2f831-3dbd-4d83-8e2f-df044bed0324",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Most work in prediction of performance is done on MOOCs and blended courses, but vcery few is done on self-paced courses. Moreover, the techniques employed are general traditional machine learning approaches without great expansions into deep learning - with explainability being pointed as one ofd the main factors behind this.",
