      "id": "63133f9e-96d8-4ac8-8919-0cda0e2b470a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Self-paced learning allows students to be more flexible in their study. However, this often comes at the expense of decreased success, especially among those students who lack the proper self-regulated learning abilities. There is some work on self-paced learning published but not a lot in terms of self-paced.",
